# Unity C# 9.0 Compatibility

- Unity client code and shared contracts must compile with C# 9.0.
- Do not use C# 10+ syntax such as file-scoped namespaces.

Example:
```csharp
// ✅ OK (C# 9.0)
namespace Game.Rpc.Contracts
{
    public interface IFoo { }
}

// ❌ NOT OK (C# 10+)
// namespace Game.Rpc.Contracts;
```
